website_summaries.verdict: When a project needs to conform to metric measurements, your tools have to as well. This set is your best best, with cuts ranging from 6 to 30 millimeters.
pros: For more precise cutting, this kit features a 5-piece set of metric hole saws, all made of thick alloy, designed to cut through multiple types of material
Combined with the spring-loaded pilot bit, this set creates a smooth cut for the most discerning of craftsman
cons: Comparatively, these saws are a bit thinner than others
Make sure that these saws are deep enough for your needs before using

product_meta.title: MOHOO 5PCS 16-30MM HSS Drill Bit Hole Saws Set Stainless High Speed Steel Metal Alloy
feature_bullets: ①Material of MOHOO hole drill bit: Mohoo 5pcs drill bit hole saw set is made of HSS(high speed steel).
②Size of 5 hole saw drill bit: 16mm/0.62" , 18.5mm/0.72" , 20mm/0.78" , 25mm/0.98" , 30mm/1.18"

③Precise and efficient: the carbide teeth of mohoo hole saw kit is able to cut clean, round holes in stainless steel, mild steel, iron, aluminum plate, alloy plate, plastic sheet, copper, brass and etc. Hole saw kits can drill about 7/9" depth for the wood, and 1/5" for the stainless steel.
④Wide application: Hole saw kit set is suitable for hand-held electric drill, vertical electric drill and mobile belt magnetic drilling machine.
⑤Special heat treatment: Through a special heat treatment, the mohoo hole saw drill bit set with sharp edge, high strength.
